---
alwaysApply: true
---
Core rules for this project:

- The product is an AI support agent for a multi-tenant SaaS platform.
- Incoming messages (email and WhatsApp) must be monitored and answered automatically.
- Retrieval and responses must use tenant-specific embeddings only.
- Tenant data and embeddings must remain isolated; no cross-tenant access.
- Users must be able to sign up, create accounts, and upload documents that become embeddings.
- Users must be able to configure the email accounts and channels to monitor.
- When a message arrives, the system must retrieve relevant tenant embeddings and generate a response using that context.
- Documentation modules must provide full, user-facing statements (not fragments).
- All functions must include docstrings.



